chunks.html_content: The State Pension age is regularly reviewed, so the results of this tool may change in the future. You can read about the results of the most recent review.
chunks.plain_content:
Check your State Pension forecast
The State Pension age is regularly reviewed, so the results of this tool may change in the future. You can read about the results of the most recent review.

chunks.html_content: You cannot use this service if you’re already getting your State Pension or if you’ve delayed (‘deferred’) claiming it.
chunks.plain_content:

You cannot use this service if you’re already getting your State Pension or if you’ve delayed (‘deferred’) claiming it.

chunks.html_content: To use this service, you’ll need to prove your identity using Government Gateway. You’ll be able to register for Government Gateway if you have not used it before.
